okay and I know what it is to sit and to sort of you know drift off for a little bit and wait for that point to come and then tune in but it won't come so you've got to kind of tune in all the time I'm afraid okay because I'm just going to talk and then I'm going to stop basically alright so we have been looking at Paul's letter to the Romans and it's been a four-part series and we have

