09:29.601 --> 09:31.184
Well, okay, so I'm free now, then.

09:31.224 --> 09:32.365
Can I just go on sinning?

09:32.606 --> 09:32.946
No.

09:33.378 --> 09:35.020
That's not the point of being free.

09:35.521 --> 09:37.884
We will still sin, but that's not the point.

09:41.209 --> 09:49.360
And he's about up here to step as it were onto the mountaintop of the book of Romans in chapter eight.

09:50.902 --> 09:52.444
We're having set that all out.

09:53.926 --> 10:02.738
He's now able to just marvel, to look around at the view and marvel at what God has done for us.

